1
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,560
I was like a fool.

2
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,680
Like a fool! Like a fool!

3
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:48,400
Every day I have to face the man

4
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,640
who killed my father

5
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,320
and force a smile at him.

6
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,410
Do you know what I've been through?

7
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:56,860
And now you actually want me to marry him?

8
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,680
My father trusted Lu Zhen'an so much.

9
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,800
He treated him like a real brother.

10
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,200
When he was at his lowest,

11
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,240
my father helped him so much.

12
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,320
And him?

13
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,120
How did he treat my father?

14
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,320
Watch your mouth.

15
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,320
What do you mean "killed"?

16
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,000
It was your father

17
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,120
who couldn't handle failure

18
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,960
and chose to end his own life.

19
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,800
That is the police's conclusion.

20
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,680
Understand?

21
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,720
You guys killed him.

22
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,560
Give me what you promised me!
Give it to me!

23
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,160
Remember.

24
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:38,000
Lu Zhen'an forced your father to death.

25
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:40,000
It has nothing to do with me.

26
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,760
And,

27
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:44,360
Lu Zhen'an also slept
with the woman I loved.

28
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:47,760
He forced me to be like a dog,

29
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,640
wagging my tail

30
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,840
and begging him.

31
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:55,600
We are in the same boat.

32
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,600
As long as you listen to me,

33
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,400
I will help you.

34
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,400
Xia?

35
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,450
What interesting things did you hear?

36
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,560
Don't touch her.

37
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:21,840
Butler Jiang,

38
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,680
let me talk to her.

39
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,760
Xia.

40
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,600
Let's go. Come with me. Let's go.

41
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:35,920
Let's go.

42
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,240
Xia?

43
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,920
Xia?

44
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:06,640
Look at me.

45
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,880
Look at me.

46
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,800
It's okay.

47
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,930
It's okay. Don't be afraid.

48
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,720
Listen to me.

49
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:21,360
What you just heard—

50
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,040
the things Butler Jiang

51
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,280
and I said—

52
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,520
were all nonsense.

53
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,080
We were lying.

54
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,340
We said it out of anger.

55
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,660
Do you understand?

56
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,800
Don't believe a word of it.

57
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,200
Nonsense!

58
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,520
Forget it.

59
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,200
Forget it.

60
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,640
Just pretend you didn't hear anything

61
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,040
and nothing happened.

62
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,680
Dad...

63
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,040
Dad...

64
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:57,800
Dad was sick.

65
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,120
He was in too much pain.

66
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,820
It had nothing to do with anyone else.

67
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,000
It had absolutely

68
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,680
nothing to do

69
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,850
with Uncle Lu and Butler Jiang.

70
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,280
Do you understand?

71
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,940
It had nothing to do with them.

72
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,240
Promise me.

73
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,760
Forget everything you just heard.

74
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,000
Xia?

75
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,280
Forget it completely.

76
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,080
Never ever

77
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,040
tell anyone.

78
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,120
Okay?

79
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,360
Including...

80
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,960
Brother Lu Fan.

81
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,200
You especially can't let him know.

82
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,260
Do you understand?

83
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,240
Xia.

84
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,040
Come on, promise me.

85
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,000
Promise me.

86
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,560
Promise me!

87
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:52,000
Was Dad really killed by them?

88
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:56,420
Are you really going to marry Lu Zhen'an?

89
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,080
I must marry him.

90
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,680
Xia.

91
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:12,280
I must continue on this path.

92
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,680
I have no way back.

93
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,720
When you grow up, you will understand me.

94
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,880
Got it?

95
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:33,840
Su Xia.

96
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,000
What's wrong?

97
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,640
They are getting married soon.

98
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,720
What about us?

99
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:53,810
Don't worry.

100
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,960
Leave it to me.

101
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,520
I'll take you somewhere.

102
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,520
Brother, where are we?

103
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:31,360
This is where I've come to be alone
since I was little.

104
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,159
A secret base?

105
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,400
Starting now,

106
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,810
it's no longer a secret.

107
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,000
This is my childhood doll.

108
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,740
That's my drawing.

109
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,040
Brother.

110
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,800
So,

111
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,600
was I once your secret too?

112
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,720
Everything in my heart is right here.

113
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:19,940
What about you?

114
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:21,960
Your secret...

115
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,640
Is it a bad memory?

116
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,440
Behave yourself!

117
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,780
Are you scared?

118
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:52,060
There is no turning back
if you want revenge.

119
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,200
This path has just begun.

120
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,570
You still have a choice.

121
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,290
I heard someone say that

122
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,000
if you want to forget bad memories,

123
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,900
you have to overwrite them with new ones.

124
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,380
In the future, I...

125
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:13,920
don't want to think about
those rainy nights anymore.

126
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,160
Think about what?

127
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,760
Don't ask,

128
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,140
and I don't want to answer.

129
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,860
You just need to...

130
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:09,060
I don't want to mention the past anymore.

131
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,500
But from now on,

132
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,240
I hope you won't lie to me again.

133
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,460
What are you doing?

134
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,720
What are you doing?

135
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,000
You must give me that thing!

136
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,680
I'm telling you!

137
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,800
Don't point at me.

138
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,360
Only I can point at you.
Don't point at me.

139
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,000
Jiang Dahai!

140
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,800
Let me go! Let me go!

141
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:05,600
Let me go!

142
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,840
Just this once!

143
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,080
Let me go!

144
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,800
Take your money and get out!

145
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,600
Alright.

146
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,320
I will get out right now.

147
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,900
What are you doing?

148
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,260
What are you doing?

149
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,120
What are you trying to do?

150
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,640
Keep your voice down.

151
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,360
If you are any louder,

152
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,480
that old dog will know everything.

153
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,480
You said it.

154
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,680
You said after you get the money,

155
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,840
you would get out.

156
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,760
Okay, don't worry.

157
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,240
The thing you want—

158
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:51,180
I have already given it to you.

159
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,840
I'm guessing

160
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,440
that you'll use the wedding

161
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,800
to expose Lu Zhen'an in public.

162
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:06,840
If I tell this plan of yours

163
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,120
to Lu Zhen'an in advance,

164
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:11,400
then wouldn't your efforts over the years

165
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,360
be in vain?

166
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,980
You are shameless!

167
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,000
Let me tell you!

168
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,440
The money I gave you is enough

169
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:24,120
for you to find young women
for the rest of your life!

170
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,180
Alright, alright.

171
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,480
Keep it down.

172
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:30,680
Those women are not like you.

173
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,600
You

174
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:35,000
are a woman who grew up
in a prestigious family.

175
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:37,840
As long as...

176
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:40,560
you let me get what I want,

177
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,840
I will take the check

178
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,810
and leave immediately.

179
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,080
Be a good girl.

180
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,000
Mrs. Lu.

181
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,560
Mrs. Lu,

182
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,520
nice working with you.
